a 3).</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6.png\" width=\"957\" height=\"1031\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Abre al menos dos bolsas de basura con una cuchilla y colÓcalas de forma plana.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />luego colÓcalas dentro de la caja que construiste. estas contendrÁn la soluciÓn<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />de nutritivos. asegÚrate de fijar las bolsas ten los contenedores, usando grapas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />o chinchetas, para evitar que el agua se salga o gotee.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-121 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7.png\" width=\"915\" height=\"1101\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-122 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.png\" width=\"1106\" height=\"1170\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-123 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.png\" width=\"1085\" height=\"1110\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<h2 class=\"page-text\"><strong><span class=\"page-number\">2 </span>VIVERO: PRIMER TRANSPLANTE</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-124 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.png\" width=\"1146\" height=\"1443\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-125 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.png\" width=\"1040\" height=\"1290\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-126 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/12.png\" width=\"1172\" height=\"1552\" />\r\