28 22:43:41','','7','','inherit','open','closed','','7-2','','','2016-12-28 22:43:41','2016-12-28 22:43:41','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(153,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:44','2016-12-28 22:43:44','','8','','inherit','open','closed','','8-2','','','2016-12-28 22:43:44','2016-12-28 22:43:44','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(154,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:46','2016-12-28 22:43:46','','9','','inherit','open','closed','','9-2','','','2016-12-28 22:43:46','2016-12-28 22:43:46','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(155,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:48','2016-12-28 22:43:48','','10','','inherit','open','closed','','10-2','','','2016-12-28 22:43:48','2016-12-28 22:43:48','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(156,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:50','2016-12-28 22:43:50','','11.1','','inherit','open','closed','','11-1','','','2016-12-28 22:43:50','2016-12-28 22:43:50','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(157,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:53','2016-12-28 22:43:53','','11.2','','inherit','open','closed','','11-2','','','2016-12-28 22:43:53','2016-12-28 22:43:53','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(158,1,'2016-12-28 22:43:56','2016-12-28 22:43:56','','header','','inherit','open','closed','','header','','','2016-12-28 22:43:56','2016-12-28 22:43:56','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/header.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(159,1,'2016-12-28 23:02:12','2016-12-28 23:02:12','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-145 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.jpg\" width=\"1072\" height=\"900\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">MATERIALES NECESARIOS:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-146 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3.1.png\" width=\"1065\" height=\"698\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-147 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3.2.png\" width=\"1065\" height=\"742\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">HERRAMIENTAS:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-148 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4.1-1.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"470\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-149 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4.2-1.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"943\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">PREPARANDO PLANCHAS DE ESPONJA</h2>\r\nUse el vaso plÁstico para definir el espacio<br class=\"hidden-767\" />y la posiciÓn de su planta. tenga en mente<br class=\"hidden-767\" />el tamaÑo de las plantas cuando crecen!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-150 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1347\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">CONSTRUYENDO EL SISTEMA DE RAÍZ FLOTANTE.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Con la madera reciclable (por ejemplo, paletas de madera) que tienes, construye una<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />caja similar al vivero – aunque este sistema es mas grande, y tendra menos plantas.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />Esto es para dar un espacio adecuado a las plantas y evitar que se den sombra unas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />a las otras y afecte su crecimiento.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-151 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-1.png\" width=\"957\" height=\"1031\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Abre al menos dos bolsas de basura con una cuchilla y colÓcalas de forma plana.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />luego colÓcalas dentro de la caja que construiste. estas contendrÁn la soluciÓn<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />de nutritivos. asegÚrate de fijar las bolsas ten los contenedores, usando grapas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />o chinchetas, para evitar que el agua se salga o gotee.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-152 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-1.png\" width=\"915\" height=\"1101\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">3 </span>TRANSPLANTANDO LOS ALMÁCIGOS</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-153 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.jpg\" width=\"864\" height=\"1082\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-154 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.jpg\" width=\"606\" height=\"1299\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">El almÁcigo estÁ listo<br class=\"hidden-767\" />para ser trasplantado<br class=\"hidden-767\" />en cualquier sistema<br class=\"hidden-767\" />hidropÓnico.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ahora puedes aÑadir<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />la soluciÓn nutritiva<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />+ el agua adentro de<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />la caja. coloque las<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />plantas encima.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-155 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.jpg\" width=\"992\" height=\"1471\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-156 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.1.jpg\" width=\"1123\" height=\"744\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-145 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.jpg\" width=\"1072\" height=\"900\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Isabel Inc.</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.isabel.io</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept, Design, Illustrations by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Antonio Scarponi / <span class=\"footer-content__text-bold\">[onceptual)evices</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.conceptualdevices.com</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">© World Food Program, 2016.</div>','SEGUNDO TRASPLANTE Y COSECHA','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 23:02:12','2016-12-28 23:02:12','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(160,1,'2016-12-28 23:05:05','2016-12-28 23:05:05','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-131 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1-1.png\" width=\"1072\" height=\"1131\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">EL VIVERO</h2>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Pasadas dos semanas, tus almÁcigos estÁn listos para su primer<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />trasplante. estos pasaran de dos a cuatro semanas en un sistema de<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />raiz flotante pequeÑo. a esta versiÓn mas pequeÑa la llamamos<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />\'vivero\'. cuando tus plantas comiencen a darse sombra unas a otras,<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />estarÁn listas para el trasplante desde el vivero al sistema mas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />grande descrito en la secciÓn 3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-115 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3.png\" width=\"1087\" height=\"691\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">MATERIALES NECESARIOS:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-116 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4.1.png\" width=\"1022\" height=\"474\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-117 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4.2.png\" width=\"976\" height=\"827\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">HERRAMIENTAS:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5.1.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"470\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-119 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5.2.png\" width=\"966\" height=\"860\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">1 </span>CONSTRUYENDO UN VIVERO</h2>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Сon la madera reciclada, contruya una caja similar a Ésta. la plancha<br class=\"hidden-767\" />de tecnopor debe de caber dentro de la caja. coloce un bloque de madera<br class=\"hidden-767\" />en cada esquina para que la plancha de tecnopor se apoye sobre ellos<br class=\"hidden-767\" />(ejemplo en pagina 3).</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6.png\" width=\"957\" height=\"1031\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Abre al menos dos bolsas de basura con una cuchilla y colÓcalas de forma plana.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />luego colÓcalas dentro de la caja que construiste. estas contendrÁn la soluciÓn<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />de nutritivos. asegÚrate de fijar las bolsas ten los contenedores, usando grapas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />o chinchetas, para evitar que el agua se salga o gotee.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-121 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7.png\" width=\"915\" height=\"1101\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-122 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.png\" width=\"1106\" height=\"1170\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-123 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.png\" width=\"1085\" height=\"1110\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<h2 class=\"page-text\"><strong><span class=\"page-number\">2 </span>VIVERO: PRIMER TRANSPLANTE</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-124 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.png\" width=\"1146\" height=\"1443\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-125 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.png\" width=\"1040\" height=\"1290\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-126 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/12.png\" width=\"1172\" height=\"1552\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Así se debería ver tu vivero cuando esta completamente plantado.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-127 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/13.1.png\" width=\"872\" height=\"764\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/13.2.png\" width=\"1058\" height=\"666\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Isabel Inc.</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.isabel.io</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept, Design, Illustrations by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Antonio Scarponi / <span class=\"footer-content__text-bold\">[onceptual)evices</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.conceptualdevices.com</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">© World Food Program, 2016.</div>','PRIMER TRANSPLANTE','','inherit','closed','closed','','133-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 23:05:05','2016-12-28 23:05:05','',133,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/133-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(163,1,'2016-12-29 16:58:08','2016-12-29 16:58:08','','p1b441f22717bn1hv9d4o1g2g131t4','','inherit','open','closed','','p1b441f22717bn1hv9d4o1g2g131t4','','','2016-12-29 16:58:08','2016-12-29 16:58:08','',76,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/p1b441f22717bn1hv9d4o1g2g131t4.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(164,1,'2016-12-29 17:51:36','2016-12-29 17:51:36','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-77 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.1.png\" width=\"1072\" height=\"945\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"page-header-1\">MATERIALES NECESARIOS:</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-81 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.3.png\" width=\"925\" height=\"890\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">1 </span>PREPARANDO EL SUSTRATO</h3>\r\nEn la hidroponÍa, se utilizan otros materiales para remplanzar la tierra.\r\nA estos materiales se les llama \'sustrato\'.\r\nlista de ejemplos abajo:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-82 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.4.png\" width=\"923\" height=\"877\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">2 </span>PLANTADO LAS SEMILLAS</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Hacer un hoyo de o.5 cm<br class=\"hidden-767\" />de profundidad con un dedo<br class=\"hidden-767\" />o un lapicero, inserte la<br class=\"hidden-767\" />semilla y cubra ligeramente</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-83 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.5.png\" width=\"809\" height=\"886\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">evite hacer los hoyos muy<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />profundos. Ya que de ser asi,<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />las semillas no recibiran la<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />luz solar necesaria. TambiÉn evite<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />hacer hoyos muy superficiales para<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />que la semilla no salga despedida<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />en el proceso de riego.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">3 </span>GERMINANDO LOS ALMÁCIGOS</h3>\r\ncoloque la bandeja en luz solar indirecta.<br class=\"hidden-767\" />pasados unos dÍas las plantas comenzaran a<br class=\"hidden-767\" />brotar. riegue gentilmente y mantenga el<br class=\"hidden-767\" />sustrato hÚmedo.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-84 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.6.png\" width=\"1071\" height=\"924\" />\r\n\r\nDEJE LA CUBIERTA PUESTA\r\nDURANTE LOS PRIMEROS 3 DÍAS\r\nO HASTA QUE BROTEN LAS PRIMERAS\r\nHOJAS..\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">riegue una vez al DÍA con<br class=\"hidden-767\" />media soluciÓn de nutrientes.<br class=\"hidden-767\" />ver pg.7 para los detalles</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">4 </span>Detalles del Cultivo Hidropónico</h3>\r\n<h4 class=\"table-header\">Ciclo de Crecimiento</h4>\r\n<div class=\"table-container\">\r\n<table class=\"page-table\" data-kind=\"Verano\">\r\n<thead class=\"page-table__thead\">\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__thead-tr\">\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Variedad de Cultivos*</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Primer Trasplante</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Segundo Trasplante</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Tiempo de Cosechar</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Lechuga</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras de hoja pequena</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">No se transplanta</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 28</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Especias</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras de hoja Asiáticas</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 7</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 35</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras abundantes</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"table-container\">\r\n<table class=\"page-table\" data-kind=\"Invierno\">\r\n<thead class=\"page-table__thead\">\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Variedad de Cultivos*</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Primer Trasplante</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Segundo Trasplante</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Tiempo de Cosechar</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Lechuga</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 21-28</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 56</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras de hoja pequena</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">No se transplanta</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Especias</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 21-28</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 56</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras de hoja Asiáticas</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Verduras abundantes</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 21-28</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\">Días 56</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<section class=\"page-section\">\r\n<h4>Instrucciones de mezcla de Solución\r\n(Usando Sales de La Molina)</h4>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__note\">Nota: Nuestra solución de nutriente contiene dos partesA y B. Siga las instrucciones de abajo para hacerlas.</div>\r\n<section class=\"page-section__solution\">\r\n<h5 class=\"page-section__solution-header\"><strong>Solución A</strong></h5>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__steps-header\">Disolver en 5 litros de agua:</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Nitrato de potasio</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Nitrato de amonio</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Superfosfato triple</em></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"page-section__solution\">\r\n<h5 class=\"page-section__solution-header\">Solución B</h5>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__steps-header\">Disolver en 2 litros de agua:</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Sulfato de magnesio</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Micronutrientes</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">1 bolsa x <em>Quelato de hierro</em></div>\r\n</section></section><section class=\"page-section\">\r\n<h4>Receta de Solución de Nutrientes</h4>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__text\">Por cada litro de agua añada 5 mL de <span class=\"page-section__text-bold\">Solución A</span> y 2 de mL <span class=\"page-section__text-bold\">Solución B</span>. Use una jeringa para tener las medidas exactas.</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__text\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-85 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.7.png\" width=\"422\" height=\"257\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__text\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>Nota: Para las plántulas, use la mitad de la solución.</em>\r\n<em>2.5 mL de Solución A y 1 mL de Solución B</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-section__text\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__header\"><strong>* Variedad de Cultivos</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"><strong><span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Lechugas:</span></strong> Romana, Francesa, Escarola, Lollo Rosso</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"><strong><span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Verduras de hoja Pequeña:</span> </strong>Rúcula, Espinaca, Lechuga Mezclada, Berro</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"><strong><span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Especias:</span> </strong>Albahaca, Cilantro, Perejil, Menta, Salvia</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"><strong><span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Verduras de hoja Asiaticas:</span> </strong>Bok Choy, Tatsoi, Hojas de Mostaza, Mizuna</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"><strong><span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Verduras Abundantes:</span> </strong>Acelgas, Espinaca, Kale</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Isabel Inc.</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.isabel.io</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept, Design, Illustrations by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Antonio Scarponi / <span class=\"footer-content__text-bold\">[onceptual)evices</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.conceptualdevices.com</div>\r\n<div c