-content/uploads/2016/12/5.png\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1347\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">CONSTRUYENDO EL SISTEMA DE RAÍZ FLOTANTE.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Con la madera reciclable (por ejemplo, paletas de madera) que tienes, construye una<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />caja similar al vivero – aunque este sistema es mas grande, y tendra menos plantas.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />Esto es para dar un espacio adecuado a las plantas y evitar que se den sombra unas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />a las otras y afecte su crecimiento.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-151 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-1.png\" width=\"957\" height=\"1031\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">Abre al menos dos bolsas de basura con una cuchilla y colÓcalas de forma plana.<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />luego colÓcalas dentro de la caja que construiste. estas contendrÁn la soluciÓn<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />de nutritivos. asegÚrate de fijar las bolsas ten los contenedores, usando grapas<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />o chinchetas, para evitar que el agua se salga o gotee.</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-152 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-1.png\" width=\"915\" height=\"1101\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"page-text\">\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\"><span class=\"page-number\">3 </span>TRANSPLANTANDO LOS ALMÁCIGOS</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-153 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.jpg\" width=\"864\" height=\"1082\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-154 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.jpg\" width=\"606\" height=\"1299\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">El almÁcigo estÁ listo<br class=\"hidden-767\" />para ser trasplantado<br class=\"hidden-767\" />en cualquier sistema<br class=\"hidden-767\" />hidropÓnico.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ahora puedes aÑadir<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />la soluciÓn nutritiva<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />+ el agua adentro de<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />la caja. coloque las<br class=\"hidden-1024\" />plantas encima.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-155 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.jpg\" width=\"992\" height=\"1471\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-156 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11.1.jpg\" width=\"1123\" height=\"744\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-145 size-full\" src=\"http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.jpg\" width=\"1072\" height=\"900\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Isabel Inc.</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.isabel.io</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Concept, Design, Illustrations by</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">Antonio Scarponi / <span class=\"footer-content__text-bold\">[onceptual)evices</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">www.conceptualdevices.com</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">© World Food Program, 2016.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"footer-content__line\">\r\n<h3 class=\"footer-content__line\">Download manual in PDF</h3>\r\n</div>','SEGUNDO TRASPLANTE Y COSECHA','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2016-12-29 20:44:54','2016-12-29 20:44:54','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(172,1,'2016-12-29 21:31:55','2016-12-29 21:31:55','','p1b440f3a9iesodc1hrl2gm6au5','','inherit','open','closed','','p1b440f3a9iesodc1hrl2gm6au5','','','2016-12-29 21:31:55','2016-12-29 21:31:55','',143,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/p1b440f3a9iesodc1hrl2gm6au5.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pd