,'2017-03-03 18:00:39','',76,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/76-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(267,1,'2017-03-03 18:02:28','2017-03-03 18:02:28','<img width=\"100%\" class=\"page-background\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.1.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Ce dont on a besoin:</h2>\r\n\r\n<img width=\"100%\" class=\"page-background\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.3.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n\r\n <h2 class=\"page-header-1\">1. Préparer le substrat</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Pour hydroponie, des autres substances remplacent la terre. Ces\r\nsubstances s\'appellent substrats. Des options suivent ci-dessous.</p>\r\n<img width=\"100%\" class=\"page-background\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.4.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n\r\n <h2 class=\"page-header-1\">2. Planter les graines</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Faire un trou de .5\r\ncentim?tres de profondeur\r\navec un doigt ou un stylo.\r\nIntroduire une graine\r\net couvrir l?g?rement.</p>\r\n<img width=\"100%\" class=\"page-background\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.5.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">\r\n?viter de faire des trous trop\r\nprofonds ou les graines ne recevront\r\npas assez de soleil. Et ?viter de\r\nfaire des trous peu profonds ou on\r\nrisque de noyer les graines quand on\r\narrose.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n <h2 class=\"page-header-1\">3. Faire germer les jeunes plants</h2>\r\n<p>Placer le bac dans une lumière de soleil diffuse.\r\nAprès quelques jours, les plants commenceront à germer.\r\nArroser suffisamment de manière à garder le substrat humide..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les jeunes plants aiment l\'humidité!\r\nCouvrir avec du plastique transparent\r\nou avec de l\'essuie tout mouillé\r\npour augmenter l\'humidité..</p>\r\n<img width=\"100%\" class=\"page-background\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.6.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n<p>\r\nLaisser couvert pour les\r\ntrois premiers jours ou jusqu\'à\r\nce qu\'on voit les nouveaux germes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">\r\nArroser une fois par jour\r\navec de la solution nutritive\r\nà moitié degré.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n <h2 class=\"page-header-1\">\r\n        4. Les details de la culture hydroponique\r\n      </h2>\r\n      <h3 class=\"table-header\">Le cycle des cultures</h3>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"table-container\">\r\n        <table class=\"page-table\" data-kind=\"l\'?t?\">\r\n          <thead class=\"page-table__thead\">\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__thead-tr\">\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Variete*<br class=\"visible-1024\"> </th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Premiere<br class=\"visible-1024\">Transplantation</th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Deuxieme <br class=\"visible-1024\">Transplantation</th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Recolte<br class=\"visible-1024\"> </th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Laitue</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   42</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jeunes legumes verts</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Pas de transplantation</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   28</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Epices</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   42</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Legumes verts asiatiques</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   21</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   35</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Legumes verts rustiques</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   42</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"table-container\">\r\n        <table class=\"page-table\" data-kind=\"l\'hiver\">\r\n          <thead class=\"page-table__thead\">\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Variete*<br class=\"visible-1024\"> </th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Premiere<br class=\"visible-1024\"> Transplantation</th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Deuxieme<br class=\"visible-1024\"> Transplantation</th>\r\n              <th class=\"page-table__th\">Recolte<br class=\"visible-1024\"> </th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Laitue</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   21-28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   56</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jeunes legumes verts</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Pas de transplantation</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   42</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Epices</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   21-28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   56</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Legumes verts asiatiques</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   42</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Legumes verts rustiques</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   14</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   21-28</td>\r\n              <td class=\"page-table__td\">Jours   56</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <section class=\"page-section\">\r\n        <h4>\r\n          Solution Mixing Instructions<br>\r\n          (Using Molina Salts)\r\n        </h4>\r\n        <div class=\"page-section__note\">\r\n          Note: Our nutrient solution contains two parts; A & B. Follow instructions below to make them.\r\n        </div>\r\n        <section class=\"page-section__solution\">\r\n          <h5 class=\"page-section__solution-header\">Solution A</h5>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__steps-header\">Disolve in 5 liters of water:</div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--green\">Nitrato de potasio</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--orange\">Nitrato de amonio</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--salmon\">Superfosfato triple</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        <section class=\"page-section__solution\">\r\n          <h5 class=\"page-section__solution-header\">Solution B</h5>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__steps-header\">Disolve in 2 liters of water:</div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--yellow\">Sulfato de magnesio</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--pink\">Micronutrientes</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"page-section__solution-step\">\r\n            1 bag x <div class=\"page-section__color-box page-section__color-box--brown\">Quelato de hierro</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      <section class=\"page-section\">\r\n        <h4>Nutrient Solution Recipes</h4>\r\n        <div class=\"page-section__text\">\r\n          For every liter of water add both 5 mL of <span class=\"page-section__text-bold\">Solution A</span> & 2 mL <span class=\"page-section__text-bold\">Solution B</span>.\r\n           Use syringe to measure exact amounts.\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img class=\"page-section__image\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.7.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-section__note\">\r\n          Note: For seedlings, use half-strength solution.<br>\r\n          2.5 mL of Solution A & 1 mL of Solution B\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"page-footnotes\">\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__header\">\r\n          * Varietes\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n          <span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Laitue:</span> laitue romaine, laitue bibb, feuille de chene, batavia\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n          <span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Jeunes legumes verts:</span> Arugula, Spinach, Mixed Lettuce, Water Cress\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n          <span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Epices:</span> Basil, Cilantro, Parsely, Mint, Sage\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n          <span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Legumes verts asiatiques:</span> Bok Choy, Tatsoi, Mustard Greens, Mizuna\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"page-footnotes__note\">\r\n          <span class=\"page-footnotes__note-header\">Legumes verts asiatiques:</span> Swiss Chard, Spinach, Kale & Chicory\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-top:10px;\"></div>\r\n<p>Concept by\r\nIsabel Inc.\r\nwww.isabel.io\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nDesign, Illustrations by\r\nAntonio Scarponi / [onceptual)evices\r\nwww.conceptualdevices.com\r\n© World Food Program, 2016.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"footer-content__line\"><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/HOW_TO_HYDROPONICS_1_III_french.pdf\">Download manual in PDF</a></h3>','CULTIVER LES JEUNES PLANTS','','publish','open','open','','cultiver-les-jeunes-plants','','','2017-03-13 08:29:54','2017-03-13 08:29:54','',0,'http://85.195.95.236/?p=267',1,'post','',0),(268,1,'2017-03-03 18:01:54','2017-03-03 18:01:54','','2017-03-03_20-51-26','','inherit','open','closed','','2017-03-03_20-51-26-2','','','2017-03-03 18:01:54','2017-03-03 18:01:54','',267,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/2017-03-03_20-51-26.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(269,1,'2017-03-03 18:01:58','2017-03-03 18:01:58','','2017-03-03_20-52-58','','inherit','open','closed','','2017-03-03_20-52-58-2','','','2017-03-03 18:01:58','2017-03-03 18:01:58','',267,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/2017-03-03_20-52-58.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(270,1,'2017-03-03 18:02:02','2017-03-03 18:02:02','','2017-03-03_20-55-24','','inherit','open','closed','','2017-03-03_20-55-24-2','','','2017-03-03 18:02:02','2017-03-03 18:02:02','',267,'http://85.195.95.236/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/2017-03-03_20-55-24.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(271,1,'2017-03-03 18:02:28','2017-03-03 18:02:28','','CULTIVER LES JEUNES PLANTS','','inherit','closed','closed','','267-revision-v1','','','2017-03-03 18:02:28','2017-03-03 18:02:28','',267,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/267-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2017-03-03 18:04:24','2017-03-03 18:04:24','','FIRST TRANSPLANT','','inherit','closed','closed','','133-revision-v1','','','2017-03-03 18:04:24','2017-03-03 18:04:24','',133,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/133-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(273,1,'2017-03-03 18:05:45','2017-03-03 18:05:45','<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">La pepiniere</h2>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Au bout de deux semaines, on peut faire la premiere\r\ntransplantation. Des jeunes plants qui vont passer les prochaines\r\ndeux a quatre semaines dans un systeme plus petit des racines\r\nflottantes. Le systeme s\'appelle la pepiniere. Une fois les plantes\r\ncommencent a se faire de l\'ombre, on peut les transplanter de la\r\npepiniere et dans le systeme plus grand represente en section 3.</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Ce dont on a boisson:</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/4.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/4.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Des outils:</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Construir la pepiniere</h2>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\" style=\"text-align: right;\">avec le bout de bois construir une boite comme celle ci-dessous. Le\r\nplateau de polystyrene dont etre a l\'interieur. Mettre un bloc de bois\r\ndans chaque coin pour soutenir le plateau.</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Avec un cutter ouvrir et aplatir au moins deux sacs poubelle pour mettre dans la\r\nboite deja construite. Le plastique doit contenir la solution nutritive. Il faut\r\nbien fixer le plastique a la boite de bois avec des agrafes ou des punaises pour\r\nassurer que la construction soit etanche (impermeable).</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">La pepiniere: la premiere transplantation</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Voila une representation d\'une installation achevee et pleinement plantee.</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/13.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/13.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\nConcept by\r\nIsabel Inc.\r\nwww.isabel.io\r\n\r\nConcept, Design, Illustrations by\r\nAntonio Scarponi / [onceptual)evices\r\nwww.conceptualdevices.com\r\n© World Food Program, 2016.\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"footer-content__line\"><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/HOW_TO_HYDROPONICS_2_III_french.pdf\">Download manual in PDF</a></h3>','FARRE LA PREMIERE TRANSPLANTATION','','publish','open','open','','farre-la-premiere-transplantation','','','2017-03-13 08:31:24','2017-03-13 08:31:24','',0,'http://85.195.95.236/?p=273',2,'post','',0),(274,1,'2017-03-03 18:05:45','2017-03-03 18:05:45','','FARRE LA PREMIERE TRANSPLANTATION','','inherit','closed','closed','','273-revision-v1','','','2017-03-03 18:05:45','2017-03-03 18:05:45','',273,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/273-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(275,1,'2017-03-03 18:07:50','2017-03-03 18:07:50','<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Ce dont on a boisson:</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-3.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-3.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Des outils:</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-4.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-4.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Preparer le plateau en polystyrene</h2>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Utiliser le gobelet plastique pour definir la\r\ndisposition des plantes (position et distance).\r\nIl faut pas oublier la taille des plantes qui poussent.</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">Construir un systeme des racines flottantes</h2>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Avec des dechets de bois (ex. des palettes) il faut construire une\r\nboite semblable a la pepiniere - sauf que ce systeme - ci est plus grand.\r\nOn va y mettre moins de plantes parce que les plantes ont besoin d\'assez\r\nde place pour ne pas faire d\'ombre.</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Avec un cutter ouvrir et aplatir au moins deux sacs poubelle pour mettre\r\ndans la boite deja construite. Le plastique doit contenir la solution\r\nnutritive. Il faut bien fixer le plastique a la boite de bois avec des\r\nagrafes ou des punaises pour assurer que la construction soit etanche (impermeable).</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">La Transplantation des jeunes Plants</h2>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p class=\"page-text\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Le jeune plant est pret pour\r\nla transplantation n\'importe\r\nquel systeme hydroponique.</p>\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">On peut maintenant\r\nverser dans la boite\r\nl\'eau avec de la\r\nsolution nutritive.\r\nMettre les plants\r\ndessus.</p>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-11.1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/3-11.2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p class=\"page-text\">Concept by\r\nIsabel Inc.\r\nwww.isabel.io</p>\r\nConcept, Design, Illustrations by\r\nAntonio Scarponi / [onceptual)evices\r\nwww.conceptualdevices.com\r\n© World Food Program, 2016.\r\n<h3 class=\"footer-content__line\"><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/HOW_TO_HYDROPONICS_3_III_french.pdf\">Download manual in PDF</a></h3>','FAIRE LA DEUXIEME TRANSPLANTATION ET LA RECOLTE','','publish','open','open','','faire-la-deuxieme-transplantation-et-la-recolte','','','2017-03-13 08:33:27','2017-03-13 08:33:27','',0,'http://85.195.95.236/?p=275',3,'post','',0),(276,1,'2017-03-03 18:07:50','2017-03-03 18:07:50','','FAIRE LA DEUXIEME TRANSPLANTATION ET LA RECOLTE','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-revision-v1','','','2017-03-03 18:07:50','2017-03-03 18:07:50','',275,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/275-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(277,1,'2017-03-03 18:12:15','2017-03-03 18:12:15','','Manual','','publish','closed','closed','','manual-es','','','2017-09-13 04:14:27','2017-09-13 04:14:27','',0,'http://85.195.95.236/?page_id=277',0,'page','',0),(278,1,'2017-03-03 18:12:15','2017-03-03 18:12:15','','Manual','','inherit','closed','closed','','277-revision-v1','','','2017-03-03 18:12:15','2017-03-03 18:12:15','',277,'http://85.195.95.236/index.php/277-revision-v1/',0,'revision','