 leaves sprout.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Water once a day with\r\nhalf-strength nutrient solution\r\nsee pg.7 for detalis</p>\r\n[embed]https://youtu.be/jq7ChzuWkQE&w=350[/embed]\r\n<h2 class=\"page-header-1\">4. Hydroponic Growing Details</h2>\r\n<h3 class=\"table-header\">Growing Cycle - Spring/Summer</h3>\r\n<div class=\"table-container\">\r\n<table class=\"page-table\" style=\"height: 206px;\" width=\"594\" data-kind=\"SUMMER\">\r\n<thead class=\"page-table__thead\">\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__thead-tr\">\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Variety*</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">First<br class=\"visible-1024\" /> Transplant</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Second<br class=\"visible-1024\" /> Transplant</th>\r\n<th class=\"page-table__th\">Harvest<br class=\"visible-1024\" /> Time</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Head Lettuce</strong></td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 28</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Baby Greens</strong></td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No transplant</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 28</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Herbs</strong></td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 14</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 28</td>\r\n<td class=\"page-table__td\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Days 42</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"page-table__tr\">\r\n<td class=\"page-table__t